2009-02-08  Manuel Pégourié-Gonnard <mpg@elzevir.fr>

	* texdoc.tlu: 
	- Display the svn rev if version ends with '+'. Display version more
	often (-h, -f).
	- Add a new level of config file and the new config option
	'lastfile_switch', allowing to install a newer version of texdoc in
	TEXMFHOME.
	- Rework print_config_files() to allow for the new 'disabled' status.
	- Remove 'abc/../' components from paths before using or displaying
	them.
	- Make the search functions case-insensitive on all platforms.

	* texdoc.cnf: Use the new last_file_switch directive.

2008-09 to 2009-01 Manuel Pégourié-Gonnard <mpg@elzevir.fr>

	* texdoc.tlu: 
	- enhancing the help message
	- stop complaining about deprecated environment variables

	* texdoc.cnf: Various updates

0.4 2008-08-14 Manuel Pégourié-Gonnard <mpg@elzevir.fr>

	* version released with TeX Live 2008

2008-07 Manuel Pégourié-Gonnard <mpg@elzevir.fr>

	* texdoc.tlu: Various changes including:
	- moved configuration from texmf.cnf to texdoc.cnf
	- added an 'alias' feature 
	- new modes 'mixed' and 'regex' 
	- file lists are now menus (select number to view results) 
	- changed the search modes to get only the more relevant results
	- /!\ zip support disabled by default (not portable) (see comments in
	source)

	* texdoc.cnf: Creation, initial alias list, comments.
	* texdoc.tex: First version.

0.3 2007-06-28 Frank Küster

	* texdoc.tlu: Various changes including:
	- added changelog
	- better OS detection for default viewer settings
	- removed some debugging code
	- -s now works in dirs without ls-R, too

0.2 2007-06-28 Frank Küster

	* texdoc.tlu: Various changes including:
	- implemented reading of configuration from texmf.cnf
	- fixed "-s" option

0.1 Frank Küster

	* texdoc.tlu: initial public release 
